BT 0 g /F4 13 Tf 72 470 Td (Once there was a clever monkey who lived in a tall tree in Eritrea.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 13 Tf 72 445 Td (One day, the monkey could not reach the fruit on a nearby branch.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 13 Tf 72 420 Td (He thought and thought. Then he used a long stick to pull the fruit closer!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 13 Tf 72 395 Td (The other animals cheered for the clever monkey.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 13 Tf 72 370 Td (When you think hard, you can solve any problem!) Tj ET
