BT 0 g /F4 13 Tf 72 470 Td (In the grasslands of Eritrea, there lived a young lion named Ari.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 13 Tf 72 445 Td (Ari was afraid of the thunder that boomed in the sky.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 13 Tf 72 420 Td (One night, a big storm came. Ari's little sister was scared too.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 13 Tf 72 395 Td (Ari took a deep breath and said, 'Don't worry, I will protect you!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 13 Tf 72 370 Td (That night, Ari learned that being brave means helping others even when you are scared.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F3 11 Tf 72 330 Td ([TIGRINYA TRANSLATION:) Tj ET
